data.description: This amazing home is an open floor plan. As you enter the spacious Foyer, there is a separate dining room with coffered ceilings. The flooring throughout the main floor is wide planked pre-engineered gorgeous. There is also an office with built in bookshelves, giving you plenty of room for work or play.  The welcoming kitchen, granite countertops, an island and a large pantry and a coffee bar will be the gathering area for any entertaining. Just off the kitchen is a covered patio for a quiet retreat and hours of privacy. There is a bedroom on the main with a full bath and 4 bedrooms upstairs. The oversized main bedroom has a sitting area. The bath has a garden tub and separate shower as well as customized closets for better storage. There is a spacious bonus room/media room just down the hall.
